In [9]:
x_train = np.asarray(x_train).reshape(42000,1024)
x_test = np.asarray(x_test).reshape(18000,1024)
x_val = np.asarray(x_val).reshape(60000,1024)
In [10]:
from tensorflow.keras.utils import to_categorical
y_train_oh= to_categorical(y_train, num_classes=10)
y_test_oh = to_categorical(y_test, num_classes=10)
y_val_oh = to_categorical(y_val, num_classes=10)
In [11]:
model = tf.keras.models.Sequential()

model.add(tf.keras.layers.BatchNormalization())
model.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(400, activation= "relu"))
model.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(200, activation= "relu"))
model.add(tf.keras.layers.Dropout(0.25))
model.add(tf.keras.layers.Dense(10,activation="softmax"))
In [12]:
earlystopping= tf.keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(monitor='val_loss', patience= 2, restore_best_weights= True)
In [13]:
model.compile(optimizer='sgd', loss='categorical_crossentropy',metrics=['accuracy'])
In [14]:
history = model.fit(x_train,y_train_oh, validation_data=(x_val,y_val_oh), epochs=20, batch_size= 50, callbacks=earlystopping)
